bodyEn:
1. I was charged an annual debit-card fee of Rs. {AMOUNT} on {TXN_DATE} (UTR {UTR}) by {BANK_NAME} even though my card is actively in use and the bank has a customer-protection directive limiting such fees. Reverse the charge.

Attachments: bank statement, sanction letter, RBI Master Circular reference.

Regards,
{USER_NAME}
Mobile: {MOBILE_NO}

bodyHi:
